  "short_description": "\"Slime Brew\" is a squishy slime merge puzzle game! Slimes of the same color combine to evolve, and as they progress, they miraculously brew delicious beer! Your goal? Create as much tasty beer as you can by merging slimes, and then drink, drink, and drink some more!",
